We have conflicting signals with negs on rates, and pos at soh peace deal, making the choice even more difficult - I will try not to rely on overnight noise (as last time, was burnt from opening when market sentiment entirely shift). Due to closure on friday, I'll make a decision on Thursday, theres a likely chance to re-enter to capitalize on the oil news, but is also dependant on how the market trends from morning to afternoon. If positioning continues to fall in a gradual sense even towards afternoon with continued elevated VIX, may skip for next week.
